cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use CRAN-PM in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "CRAN-PM: Cross-Resolution Attention Network for high-resolution PM2.5 forecasting"
abstract: >-
  CRAN-PM is a multi-scale deep learning model for short-range (1-4 day)
  PM2.5 surface concentration forecasting at high spatial resolution
  over Europe. It combines ERA5 meteorology, CAMS chemistry and
  high-resolution elevation through a cross-resolution attention bridge.
type: software
authors:
